Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.85,0:00:10.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The 7th Kyotouryuu head, Yasuri Shichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.21,0:00:17.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The army general director in support of critical tasks under direct control of Yanari Shogun of the Owari Shogunate,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.03,0:00:18.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Togame the Strategian.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.34,0:00:25.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,These two have begun their journey to collect Shikizaki Kiki's perfected Deviant Blades.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.02,0:00:33.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It is said those who wield those 12 swords can rule the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.67,0:00:38.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,After obtaining Zettou Kanna, previously held by Maniwa Koumori,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.60,0:00:44.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,they have arrived at the city of Kyoto to prepare for the journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.89,0:00:48.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you shocked at such an unfamiliar sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.36,0:00:51.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, there's people everywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.27,0:00:53.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,With this many, I really can't tell anyone apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.52,0:00:55.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to tell them apart or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:00:56.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.11,0:00:57.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.40,0:01:02.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you try to study every person that crosses your way, you'll go crazy in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.15,0:01:05.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I've gone crazy already, Togame.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.43,0:01:07.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.22,0:01:10.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell you apart from others your height...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.81,0:01:12.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How bad can you get...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.86,0:01:13.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.55,0:01:13.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.86,0:01:15.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.36,0:01:20.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.80,0:01:22.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.78,0:01:25.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Think of him as a bear or some other animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.27,0:01:26.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.45,0:01:30.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.17,0:01:35.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ask me that, I'd have to say everything about you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.33,0:01:38.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,With that outfit you do look a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:40.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.18,0:01:43.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Staring a gift horse in the mouth, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.65,0:01:46.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need anything like this to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.57,0:01:47.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll make it hard to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.87,0:01:52.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,People were looking at you as if you were naked back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:53.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really care.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.54,0:01:55.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a problem for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.13,0:01:59.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Walking along with a young, naked man in the depths of winter?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.20,0:02:01.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What would people think of a woman like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.86,0:02:02.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What would they think?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.98,0:02:09.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They'd see me as some dominatrix and harass me anywhere I go by throwing rocks as we pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.82,0:02:11.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:14.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you agree then go find some clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.23,0:02:16.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Living on the mainland comes with a lot of hassles...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.81,0:02:19.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet everyone lives through them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.65,0:02:21.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you decided what you'd like?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.63,0:02:22.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.55,0:02:24.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take this and this and that and that and that please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.63,0:02:26.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that many?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.10,0:02:27.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need that many.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.55,0:02:29.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They're for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:33.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you already have a lot of clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.28,0:02:35.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Learn to appreciate a lady's fashion sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.32,0:02:36.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.96,0:02:38.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one I don't get.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.07,0:02:40.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that getup?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.90,0:02:42.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not naked so it's fine, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.65,0:02:48.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose it qualifies as original, and you could say it's chic to flaunt such a weather-defying outfit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.66,0:02:50.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm not a fan of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.96,0:02:54.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't get this whole like and dislike stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.63,0:02:59.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:02.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sometimes you run into people like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.98,0:03:04.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.15,0:03:05.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:06.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:08.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I will protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.74,0:03:11.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My, what pretty clothes you're wearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:15.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't wanna die, you know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.57,0:03:17.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of handing anything over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:23.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, if you guys don't want to die, keep your swords sheathed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.94,0:03:26.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.49,0:03:31.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I told you to keep them sheathed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.09,0:03:32.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:40.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys would be dead if you were a little better at using those swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:44.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyotouryuu hidden art...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.81,0:03:46.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.88,0:03:49.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you finishing them off?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:50.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:51.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.49,0:03:53.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a mainland custom?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.49,0:03:55.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's common sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.65,0:04:00.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They may be bad guys, but that doesn't mean you can just slaughter them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.14,0:04:04.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.45,0:04:08.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't stopped him you really would have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:10.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What a hassle...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:14.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A man who knows no one, a woman who closed her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.22,0:04:17.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus their journey of hardship began.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.03,0:05:59.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a month since they started their search for Shikizaki Kiki's Deviant Blades.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.37,0:06:04.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Togame and Shichika have headed to Inaba to find the second sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.39,0:06:08.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so rough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.25,0:06:10.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how to hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.15,0:06:20.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do we have to keep doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.34,0:06:24.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Until you're able to recognize me clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.89,0:06:29.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be troublesome if you don't learn to distinguish people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.35,0:06:30.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.15,0:06:36.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't want to be mistaken for an assassin and killed if I call out to you as a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:37.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.97,0:06:42.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm trying to learn your exact color and scent right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:44.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot, you're not allowed to bite, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:46.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll injure me if you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:47.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How about licking?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:48.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're allowed to lick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.87,0:06:51.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, go ahead and lick me to remember my taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:53.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop squirming around though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:55.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When you pull on my hair it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.29,0:06:56.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.45,0:07:01.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Training is a funny thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:04.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, we'll be in Inaba tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.41,0:07:07.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.79,0:07:08.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's it called again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.30,0:07:11.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Gekoku Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:13.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're aiming for Zantou Namakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:13.81,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Blunt, the Decapitator
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.81,0:07:15.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a pretty weak-sounding name...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:17.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Shikizaki's sense of irony.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.96,0:07:21.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The main feature of Zantou is its unparalleled sharpness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:25.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll supposedly cut through absolutely anything effortlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.52,0:07:33.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So wait, what would happen if you tried to use Zantou to cut that tough Zettou?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.03,0:07:36.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say for sure without trying,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.15,0:07:41.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but probably, the one that is less complete would yield.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.17,0:07:47.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Zantou was made later, so if it came down to it, Zettou would probably be cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:51.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a reason I chose to go after Namakura next.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.62,0:07:53.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Our opponent this time is a swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:55.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A swordsman would be an easier opponent than a ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.44,0:08:00.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a ronin named Uneri Ginkaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.44,0:08:00.11,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Masterless samurai
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:02.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe you could call him a castle lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:08.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, when Shogun Kyuu ordered the sword hunt,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:12.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,its owner was a samurai serving the Tottori feudal lord named Uneri Kinkaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.52,0:08:17.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But in an act unbefitting of a samurai, Kinkaku refused to turn over Zantou.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.26,0:08:20.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"It belongs to me" he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.94,0:08:28.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, he used Zantou to repulse the army Shogun Kyuu sent after him, killing over 10,000 soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.07,0:08:29.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,10,000?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.28,0:08:34.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Its current owner, Uneri Ginkaku, is supposedly his 10th generation descendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.31,0:08:41.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Entrance front the through in walk just to ninja a as embarrassing pretty it's but,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.51,0:08:44.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,helped be can't it case this in, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.30,0:08:46.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Myself introduce me let.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:51.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Corps Maniwa the of heads 12 the of one, Shirasagi Maniwa I'm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.63,0:08:55.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shirasagi talk-reverse" me call people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:09:07.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Namakura Zantou, anything through slice to able as heralded is that sword fearsome the — that taking be I'll.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:11.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Lonely get I'll or me ignore don't, now hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.67,0:09:15.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Much that it see to want really you do or?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.17,0:09:21.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Know you, anyone to arts ninja my show just don't I,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:23.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,now on come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:34.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to tell me that your "reverse talk" ninja art allows you to keep jabbering on after being sliced in half?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:37.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Woah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:38.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-When did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:40.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Ginkaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:43.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiken: Zerosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.89,0:09:48.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I got the tatami mats dirty...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.95,0:09:57.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I heard about this place from my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:09:59.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've secretly been looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.22,0:10:03.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Inaba today is no longer like what you've heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:09.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The Inaba desert started rapidly expanding about 5 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:10.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's since swallowed up the whole Tottori domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.21,0:10:14.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, it's an uninhabitable land.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:18.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So what's that Uneri Ginkaku guy doing in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:20.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, he's the lord of a castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.71,0:10:22.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:26.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it pointless being a feudal lord in a land where no one lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.79,0:10:31.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd think so, but of all the servants the Shogunate has sent there to scout it out,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.51,0:10:33.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,not a single one has returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:35.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut first, ask later...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.13,0:10:39.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He might have been lured by the poison of Shikizaki's sword,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.52,0:10:42.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,or he might have some other reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.01,0:10:44.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So basically you have no clue?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.14,0:10:46.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say you specialize in brain work?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:49.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything and everything I do is part of my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:51.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You needn't bother asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:52.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.81,0:10:56.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, you need to come up with a catchphrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.01,0:10:57.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A catchphrase?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:10:58.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.89,0:10:59.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.42,0:11:00.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:07.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I went ahead and wrote about your successful venture last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.44,0:11:10.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that report thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.18,0:11:15.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, like you asked, I took down that ninja guy in a flashy way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.02,0:11:23.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,True as that is, I didn't actually see how flashy it was, so I couldn't write about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.94,0:11:26.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I went out of the way to do as you asked too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.76,0:11:28.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:30.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't write about what I didn't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.65,0:11:36.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, it isn't really a huge problem, since you'll have more opportunities in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.56,0:11:43.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly Shichika, when I was writing about how we obtained Kanna, I noticed one important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:45.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Important thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:47.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a weak personality!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.42,0:11:52.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,...is how I figure I should react, but what's the problem, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:54.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So naive!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:55.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an amateur?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.32,0:11:57.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,At everything but the sword arts. {'sword arts' -> 'my art'?}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.42,0:12:00.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't afford to be so selfish from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.41,0:12:00.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.46,0:12:07.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how I worded the report, that Maniwa Koumori ninja stood out more than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.85,0:12:10.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I rewrote it and rewrote it but the result was the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:14.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just couldn't make you stand out more than Koumori.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:15.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:19.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When I finished the final revision and read it over,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:23.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,no matter what, the only impression I got of you was that of a half-naked idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.72,0:12:25.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I said wait a second, Togame-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:32.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'd lose in character to a guy who pulls swords from his mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:35.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I won the fight, so there shouldn't be any problem, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.47,0:12:40.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, if you lose in fighting it'd be a problem, but it's also a problem if you lose in character.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.62,0:12:44.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your personality has almost nothing interesting about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.48,0:12:46.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't hold back, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.43,0:12:49.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I did, would I be able to write a captivating report?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:52.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what kind of battle is she fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:57.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, there are other ninja with far stronger personalities than Koumori, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.86,0:13:00.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just among the ones I know, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.10,0:13:03.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a ninja called Shirasagi who speaks backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:07.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what, he'll speak with his words reversed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.46,0:13:09.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.44,0:13:12.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's trying his utmost not to be boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.32,0:13:16.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do ninja have to take that into consideration too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:17.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Those "Maniwani" guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:19.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maniwani?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.19,0:13:20.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you shortened it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:23.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Maniwa corps" is kind of hard to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:25.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bite my tongue on it eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:27.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maniwani...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.90,0:13:28.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:29.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.84,0:13:31.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kind of cute. I approve.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.64,0:13:32.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.34,0:13:33.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.53,0:13:35.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the first intelligent thing you've said.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:36.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.59,0:13:40.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The readers will get to know you and come to understand your outlook.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.12,0:13:43.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your report sounds like a lot of work...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:45.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally understand, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:49.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's true our opponents are extremely eccentric,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.87,0:13:55.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,so asking you to try to reach their level is probably too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.04,0:13:56.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so Shichika,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.14,0:14:00.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,having said that, you still have to put in a minimum amount of effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.89,0:14:05.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That said, for the time being we'll focus on your catchphrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:07.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really something you decide by thinking about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.62,0:14:12.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it has to give the reader a kind of "wow, this guy isn't normal" impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.23,0:14:14.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really mind if they think I'm normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:17.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't have that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.01,0:14:20.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll happen if they get so bored they stop reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.66,0:14:24.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Does a report have to be that interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.41,0:14:25.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.70,0:14:30.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The genius swordsman Sabi Hakuhei's catchphrase is quite good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.62,0:14:34.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As annoying as it is to speak well of someone who betrayed me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:37.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,even so, I must give recognition where recognition is due.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.72,0:14:39.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask what it is just for reference.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.28,0:14:44.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'll have you fall for me."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.87,0:14:49.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd die if I had a catchphrase like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:50.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.19,0:14:52.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There is something I'm always saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.98,0:14:53.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:55.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, that "Such a hassle!" thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.88,0:14:57.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheerio!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.63,0:15:03.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot, what kind of apathetic phrase is that to set up your character with?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:07.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about what it's like for me to write about such a stagnant character.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.56,0:15:11.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What happens if I lose my will to write halfway through?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:11.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.94,0:15:17.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place, if I described you constantly saying "it's a hassle it's a hassle!" while we're collecting swords,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:20.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,you'd come across as doing it unwillingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.57,0:15:21.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So I should work enthusiastically?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:23.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.50,0:15:28.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I just want to avoid looking like I forced you to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:31.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty self-centered, aren't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.72,0:15:35.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though that said, I can't just come up with something on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.39,0:15:36.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.52,0:15:40.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you'd say that, so I came up with some in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:43.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well I'm sure you'll like at least one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:47.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have the privilege of picking out the final candidate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.62,0:15:49.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pick whatever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.08,0:15:52.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a pretty intrusive privilege...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.09,0:15:55.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, assuming I like any.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:55.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.77,0:15:59.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I've prepared some really cool catchphrases.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.35,0:16:03.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hey, the gods loves no one more than me, yeah?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.18,0:16:06.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"H-Hey"...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.08,0:16:12.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say that you had brain power to make up for your lack of fighting prowess?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.79,0:16:13.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:17.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A dumb person couldn't come up with that catchphrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:20.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true it has a certain evil ring to it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.52,0:16:25.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fundamentally, a catchphrase is meant to provoke your opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.03,0:16:30.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like pointing out the difference in status, or expressing your complete self-confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.54,0:16:37.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you announce your omnipotence beforehand, when you win, it'll look like an easy victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:41.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like I'd just become another bad guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.47,0:16:47.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Frankly, it'd help me out if you were a little more of a bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:55.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I demonstrated the ability to handle a tough nut or a rowdy smartass, my own standing would improve.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.12,0:16:59.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In that respect, you're a little too nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:00.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So selfish...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.24,0:17:04.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently you're looking to get exiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:13.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would a guy who was exiled for 20 years himself say that so proudly to someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.69,0:17:14.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.59,0:17:16.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly why it sounds so convincing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:19.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't need that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:22.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a picky guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.17,0:17:27.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Does she intend to continue this pointless conversation the whole way there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:31.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think too much over the next one but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.01,0:17:35.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"However, by that point you'll have been torn into pieces."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:37.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.08,0:17:38.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, whatever, that's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.83,0:17:40.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:42.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I said that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.22,0:17:46.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"However, by that point you'll have been torn into pieces."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.24,0:17:48.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.17,0:17:50.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're okay with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.64,0:17:52.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:57.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a choice I was expecting to really push while I was thinking it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.38,0:18:00.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though that said, it's certainly a work I'm proud of.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:03.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm totally shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.25,0:18:04.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It matches me so well!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.42,0:18:05.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:11.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This idea was born from your super ultimate "Shichika Hachiretsu" move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:12.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.84,0:18:14.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, you can go ahead and thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.83,0:18:16.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You made my day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.82,0:18:18.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.96,0:18:21.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well if you like it then that's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.84,0:18:27.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though because you were so picky, this discussion went on longer than I thought it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.18,0:18:31.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That said, not so long that we have to rush or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:34.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,At this pace, we'll reach our destination around evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.97,0:18:35.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.78,0:18:39.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,However, by that point you'll have been torn into pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.33,0:18:40.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheerio!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.23,0:18:44.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you not think?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:46.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so confusing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.94,0:18:51.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, that "cheerio!" I've been using is my catchphrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.62,0:18:54.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see... I didn't really notice...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.67,0:19:00.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Cheerio" is a popular phrase in the Satsuma domain in Kyushu.{Norg: we gonna add 'in Kyuushuu' or does that make it too long? Also 藩!=県}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:04.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not so much in the dialect, but more like part of the culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.17,0:19:12.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any particular connection to Kyushu, but the expression "cheerio" just seems kind of cute to me. {Norg: took out the battle cry bit.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.99,0:19:18.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually quite proud of the effect it has when combined with my appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.07,0:19:22.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it'll catch on once I submit my report to the Shogunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:22.60,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, as you are aware,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.60,0:19:27.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,the phrase originating from the Satsuma domain used to raise one's spirits is "chesuto".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:32.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The expression "cheerio" which Togame uses is a foreign word meaning "goodbye".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.53,0:19:43.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The story of when she notices her mistake and loses herself with embarrassment is yet some months away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.75,0:19:54.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakuhei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.69,0:19:56.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be taking that sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:20:02.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, have become lost to this sword's magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.22,0:20:03.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.93,0:20:09.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have you fall for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.55,0:20:14.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:24.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up, you're walking too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:26.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.54,0:20:29.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not used to walking with anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.87,0:20:32.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're heavy because you're wearing too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.52,0:20:33.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.74,0:20:35.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't frivolously call a lady heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.45,0:20:39.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well you're definitely light,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:41.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but isn't it hard to move with all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.58,0:20:43.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Once again, you're an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.31,0:20:45.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Women use different muscles to stay fashionable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.40,0:20:47.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Women have such body parts?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.50,0:20:50.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Parts that a backwater barbarian like you wouldn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.57,0:20:53.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't care about fashion or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.26,0:20:56.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Clothes just get in the way when you wear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.80,0:21:01.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already given up on trying to get you to clothe your upper body.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.36,0:21:03.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just don't take off anything from your lower half, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:05.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to travel with a pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.96,0:21:07.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.27,0:21:11.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've taken a liking to this hakama that you bought me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.27,0:21:10.89,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: A hakama is the pants-like thing he's wearing
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.01,0:21:13.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy to move and easy to fight in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.40,0:21:16.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ease of movement and ease of fighting are different?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:18.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah they're different.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.72,0:21:21.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So is there still a ways to go till we get to Gekoku Castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.78,0:21:25.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be night soon, and that'd be inconvenient for you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.38,0:21:26.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:30.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Letting a girl sleep outdoors in the desert would be a total waste of her fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.11,0:21:31.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the problem here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.23,0:21:34.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell left this here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.10,0:21:41.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Maniwani's... Maniwa Shirasagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.06,0:21:49.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.35,0:21:50.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How... { didn't we see it till now?}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.48,0:21:53.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a camouflage caused by a mirage in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.25,0:21:55.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't see it till you get this close.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.20,0:21:58.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Inaba desert's Gekoku castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.75,0:22:01.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Strong offense, easy to defend.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.61,0:22:06.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Most people don't know about it, but it's famous among certain groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.06,0:22:09.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That was quite a shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.34,0:22:10.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.21,0:22:12.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd try surprising you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.06,0:22:17.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So why's his body discarded like this outside the castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.48,0:22:23.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently the 12 Maniwa corps leaders are competing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.64,0:22:28.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a race to collect Shikizaki Kiki's 12 perfected Deviant Blades.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.70,0:22:38.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Presumably, Shirasagi learned that Uneri Ginkaku of Gekoku castle holds Zantou Namakura, and came to take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.40,0:22:40.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And then got cut down instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.13,0:22:44.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,To think a Maniwa corps head was brought down like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.17,0:22:46.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've beaten a Maniwani head too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.86,0:22:50.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In your case, you were merely blessed with luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.06,0:22:53.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's think of it positively...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.44,0:22:58.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The Maniwani who got here first failed to get Zantou.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.15,0:23:01.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on your perspective, that could be a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.52,0:23:07.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If Shirasagi had succeeded in obtaining the Deviant Blade, we'd have come here for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.70,0:23:09.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, that is positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.55,0:23:16.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But because of this guy's failed attempt, the castle lord will be on his guard now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.29,0:23:18.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Worst case, he might even have run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.37,0:23:20.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.69,0:23:27.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uneri Ginkaku is the man who didn't leave this land even after the entirety of Inaba turned to desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.00,0:23:31.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, by the looks of Shirasagi here,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.47,0:23:35.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uneri has complete faith in his own skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.11,0:23:38.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fleeing before an approaching foe wouldn't even cross his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.81,0:23:41.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he's a stronger opponent than we thought, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.25,0:23:47.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We could also come back later, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.17,0:23:48.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.83,0:23:55.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't afford to waste any time now that the Maniwa corps are moving so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.81,0:24:00.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite the opposite Shichika, I'm glad this happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.13,0:24:08.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got something interesting to write in my report now, thanks to Maniwa Shirasagi giving us this opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.71,0:24:15.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,To be able to report that we took the Deviant Blade from the swordsman who cut down Maniwa Shirasagi the traitor...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.01,0:24:17.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How satisfying!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.31,0:24:23.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And most importantly, now I don't have to write down any tedious backwards talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.55,0:24:25.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.19,0:24:34.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And anyway, are you suggesting I write about us turning tail even though we're so well prepared?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.87,0:24:36.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, that certainly is positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.93,0:24:37.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.87,0:24:41.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I fell for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.21,0:24:50.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it dangerous for you to go first?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.21,0:24:53.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one fighting, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.56,0:24:58.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you plan to take on Uneri Ginkaku yourself first?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.10,0:24:59.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.38,0:25:02.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You know very well how good I am at fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.71,0:25:06.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be easier for him to defeat me than to rip a paper screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.69,0:25:08.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you say that so proudly...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.69,0:25:15.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, apparently you're misunderstanding this part of the process, so I'll make it clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.74,0:25:18.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't come here as thieves.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.99,0:25:25.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't just run in, swords swinging, and pillage it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.85,0:25:28.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to follow proper procedures and negotiate.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.88,0:25:32.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... "procedures", like at a government office?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.67,0:25:35.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's say that's how it is for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.28,0:25:39.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's all it takes, you don't really need me do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.52,0:25:47.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost a certainty that anyone who would consume the poison of Shikizaki's swords is insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.11,0:25:50.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So basically, you're not expecting that negotiation can settle this to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.65,0:25:51.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.79,0:25:53.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to consider the chance that it can.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.69,0:25:57.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Take for example the case where the sword owner happens to be a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.16,0:25:59.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.57,0:26:04.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we have the backing of the Shogunate, we won't be punished even if we do kill people.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.71,0:26:09.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't make it okay to senselessly cut people up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.36,0:26:11.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's out the way, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.07,0:26:18.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a suspiciously obvious screen...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.15,0:26:20.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,which means there's something here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.25,0:26:25.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, don't just open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.06,0:26:26.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.80,0:26:39.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be Uneri Ginkaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.58,0:26:47.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the army general director in support of critical tasks under direct control of Yanari Shogun of the Owari Shogunate,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.53,0:26:48.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Togame the Strategian.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.42,0:26:54.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That sword appears to be Zantou Namakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.05,0:26:55.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.77,0:26:57.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What a racket.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.83,0:27:00.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true I am Uneri Ginkaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.75,0:27:03.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to shout like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.48,0:27:05.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.54,0:27:06.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.89,0:27:10.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is a big shot from the Shogunate here in the desert?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.59,0:27:14.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you consider handing over Zantou?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.57,0:27:17.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I'm prepared to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.44,0:27:20.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll provide anything the shogunate can offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.22,0:27:30.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, just a bit earlier some fake-looking ninja came along and said something similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.37,0:27:31.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.96,0:27:33.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A friend of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.44,0:27:36.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's no friend of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.31,0:27:39.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're different from that ninja scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.28,0:27:42.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to make a fair trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.19,0:27:48.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, even given that it's a single sword, I'm well aware of its value.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.83,0:27:54.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that it's not something you can just replace.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.19,0:28:01.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I'd like you to consider this offer for the sake of the Shogunate — no, for the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.20,0:28:06.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't a single sane person who talks about a unified country these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.50,0:28:11.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.41,0:28:17.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you don't wish to continue living aimlessly in the desert like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.09,0:28:21.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have any ambitions, I can assist you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.16,0:28:23.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Both in public and in the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.82,0:28:27.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you'd support a ronin like myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.15,0:28:32.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grateful for the offer, but I've heard there's a bounty on my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.81,0:28:35.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I can release you from that burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.92,0:28:38.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have anything you desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.39,0:28:41.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Uneri!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.45,0:28:45.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't quite hear you properly this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.19,0:28:47.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you come a bit closer?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.50,0:28:55.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, isn't it rude to speak to a swordsman from across a door?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.46,0:29:00.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know exactly how important you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.04,0:29:05.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but that isn't the right attitude for someone asking a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.63,0:29:08.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.69,0:29:09.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.96,0:29:19.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyotouryuu: Lily!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.51,0:29:28.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.93,0:29:29.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.99,0:29:33.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I can calm down after suddenly being kicked, you idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.15,0:29:35.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A mysterious force suddenly pulling me backwards...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.40,0:29:38.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought aliens were abducting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.10,0:29:40.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You certainly have quite the imagination...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.97,0:29:47.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So that was Iainuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.97,0:29:47.97,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Kneeling sword draw
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.46,0:29:53.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't been wearing as much clothing, I'd be...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.72,0:29:58.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure it'd be the same either ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.19,0:30:01.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.00,0:30:06.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time my Zerosen has been evaded since I inherited Zantou.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.85,0:30:09.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who's shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.53,0:30:15.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd heard Iainuki was a supreme sword technique, but to think it's that fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.73,0:30:21.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So with my shock and your shock, we're even.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.28,0:30:23.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uneri!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.20,0:30:25.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand what you've just done?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.50,0:30:31.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The same goes for you too, bringing along such a skilled big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.64,0:30:35.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You intended to do things by force from the start, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.39,0:30:37.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.15,0:30:40.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look like this guy's little sister??
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.25,0:30:42.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What part of me looks like a "little sister"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.36,0:30:52.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My ancestors refused to give up this sword to their own masters, let alone the Shogunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.78,0:30:58.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I simply said "here you go" and gave it up to you, I'd be the laughing stock of my dead fathers.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.45,0:31:01.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you afraid of losing that sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.07,0:31:08.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't reach that level of speed with that Zerosen move of yours without it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.75,0:31:10.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So are you afraid of losing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.76,0:31:12.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And what if I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.22,0:31:13.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.97,0:31:18.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking to myself that that must be the limit for sword users.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.34,0:31:27.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you a swordsman yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.01,0:31:29.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I am most definitely a swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.43,0:31:35.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In which case, no further words are needed, as swordsmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.53,0:31:39.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want this sword, stop talking and come get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.80,0:31:44.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll stop talking and fight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.78,0:31:46.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stubbornness?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.46,0:31:48.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.04,0:31:54.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You may be confident after saving that woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.20,0:31:56.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but that wasn't my full strength just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.17,0:32:02.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Zerosen at full speed is faster than light.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.48,0:32:04.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.02,0:32:06.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Togame.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.34,0:32:08.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to confirm something.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.81,0:32:09.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.30,0:32:11.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.38,0:32:13.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a bit of strategizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.25,0:32:16.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be back soon, so take a nap or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.99,0:32:22.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm back, I'll have you show me your full speed Zerosen or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.89,0:32:27.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Close the screen on your way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.30,0:32:31.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.89,0:32:36.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't tell me your name yet, big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.03,0:32:44.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the 7th Kyotouryuu head...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.38,0:32:45.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yashuri Shichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.50,0:32:50.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My tongue slipped...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.58,0:33:02.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look so upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.25,0:33:04.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't done that you'd be in two pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.50,0:33:06.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't look upset, 'kay!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.76,0:33:07.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"kay"?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.42,0:33:09.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.21,0:33:12.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't look upset!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.05,0:33:15.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're ridiculously childish sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.46,0:33:17.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How old are you, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.72,0:33:19.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}are{\i0\fscx133} {\fscx100}older than me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.51,0:33:22.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.17,0:33:25.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly Shichika, what did you want to confirm?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.69,0:33:29.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see a good reason for you to have stopped the fight at that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.10,0:33:34.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see if he'd let us.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.16,0:33:36.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If he'd let us?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.97,0:33:42.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, whether he'd chase us or not as we left.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.97,0:33:45.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But he let us go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.20,0:33:47.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.52,0:33:53.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment you crossed the boundary into that room, he attacked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.51,0:34:00.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking at it the other way, he won't attack us as long as we don't enter that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.95,0:34:05.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That secluded room is optimal for him to ambush his foes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.67,0:34:06.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.96,0:34:11.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why Maniwa Shirasagi had no choice but to face him up front.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.65,0:34:14.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That room is Uneri Ginkaku's absolute territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.96,0:34:19.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we should find a way to drag him out of that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.90,0:34:22.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.94,0:34:25.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,First, you'll enter the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.53,0:34:27.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll enter...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.96,0:34:31.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, falling prey to Zerosen, you get cut in two.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.17,0:34:32.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.49,0:34:35.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Since he can't just abandon your corpse,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.06,0:34:41.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,he'll have to leave the castle to dispose of you, like with Maniwa Shirasagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.04,0:34:42.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.31,0:34:44.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I get him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.14,0:34:45.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheerio!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.51,0:34:48.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get cut in two for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.40,0:34:52.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I was thinking it might not work.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.45,0:34:53.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.88,0:34:59.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, even if we give up on luring him out, I still have a plan, Togame.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.89,0:35:03.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I get split into two in this plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.49,0:35:10.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have to face your opponent directly, just do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.51,0:35:11.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichika,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.68,0:35:14.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,if that's the conclusion you came to, I'm going to be angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.54,0:35:17.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you've been angry the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.00,0:35:17.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mock me!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.96,0:35:19.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.05,0:35:23.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think just winning today isn't good enough to win tomorrow's battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.14,0:35:30.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't just win by luck like with Koumori.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.36,0:35:35.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's unexpectedly serious, coming from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.40,0:35:40.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to protect the swords, as well as you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.48,0:35:49.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-If you understand that then stop coming up with plans that involve splitting me in half!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.48,0:35:52.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, I'll ask that you stand behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.10,0:35:55.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As insurance, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.35,0:36:02.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you're already aware, but I have no skills by which to cover your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.53,0:36:04.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.11,0:36:05.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichika...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.77,0:36:07.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.27,0:36:12.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't express it very well, but I want you to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.31,0:36:20.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, people with something to protect are strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.01,0:36:26.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He said Kyotouryuu...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.75,0:36:29.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A martial art based on swordsmanship?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.19,0:36:33.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A swordsman gains nothing by discarding his sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.47,0:36:36.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What a creepy style.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.95,0:36:38.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.47,0:36:40.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no use thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.47,0:36:44.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I need only protect this castle and this sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.25,0:36:46.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.49,0:36:58.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone ran from the desert, abandoning their homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.58,0:37:03.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps, if I wasn't the last one,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.06,0:37:05.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd have been able to leave Inaba too.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.65,0:37:10.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, leaving was never an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.49,0:37:13.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not allowed to be indecisive.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.33,0:37:18.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this my anchor to this land, to this sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.08,0:37:22.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It truly is an obsession.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.85,0:37:26.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A swordsman needs something to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.11,0:37:29.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Without that, he cannot fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.06,0:37:38.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.48,0:37:41.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.51,0:37:42.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.53,0:37:43.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.80,0:37:48.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come up with a counter to my Zerosen?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.55,0:37:50.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.38,0:37:56.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What, Kyotouryuu even has a counter for Iainuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.55,0:38:02.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if the opponent is someone at your level, it'll probably work.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.98,0:38:07.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,For this technique, the faster the opponent's sword moves, the more effective it becomes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.79,0:38:14.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyotouryuu, seventh stance: Iris.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.31,0:38:17.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that ridiculously obvious pose?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.39,0:38:20.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he had a counter, but that's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.96,0:38:23.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears I'm not being taken seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.12,0:38:24.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyotouryuu...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.97,0:38:27.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,clearly not a worthy opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.18,0:38:30.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot, he's just taunting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.64,0:38:34.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.28,0:38:36.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright then, on your marks...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.33,0:38:38.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Get set...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.24,0:38:38.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.68,0:38:40.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The distance is three steps!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.37,0:38:42.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.17,0:38:44.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.19,0:38:45.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.95,0:38:46.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Zerosen!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.67,0:38:50.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyotouryuu: Rose!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.57,0:38:53.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You got him?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.95,0:38:55.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it was too weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.68,0:39:00.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll admit that was a good feint with your footwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.50,0:39:03.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to cut at a phantom illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.50,0:39:06.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But why did you hold back?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.93,0:39:08.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What does he mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.13,0:39:12.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Rose would have finished him if I hadn't held back.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.50,0:39:15.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,His sword pressure caught me off guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.74,0:39:17.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.02,0:39:20.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,To have his lack of real battle experience show now of all times...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.72,0:39:22.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichika!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.91,0:39:22.21,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.81,0:39:24.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay behind me!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.46,0:39:25.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.72,0:39:28.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I can just sit by after your plan failed?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.38,0:39:31.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That surprised me...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.52,0:39:35.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you've done it twice, I'm sure it isn't dumb luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.09,0:39:38.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm completely awake now, Kyotouryuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.56,0:39:42.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the best I've felt since I was born screaming into this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.24,0:39:45.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome, and good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.40,0:39:48.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And good night to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.45,0:39:54.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm aware that what you did was extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.99,0:39:58.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't think the same thing will work again.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.75,0:40:01.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurting him was a bad move...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.86,0:40:04.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Zerosen formation: Five lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.59,0:40:09.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Five attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.32,0:40:16.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, it won't matter whether you speed up or slow down.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.46,0:40:19.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll easily overcome any small errors like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.99,0:40:23.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You were hiding that the whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.65,0:40:25.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.01,0:40:27.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.82,0:40:31.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.68,0:40:33.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.22,0:40:35.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He cut himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.58,0:40:36.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.64,0:40:42.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the technique Uneri Kinkaku used to kill 10,000 soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.43,0:40:45.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Observe, Kyotouryuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.38,0:40:51.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When my blood flows into the sheath and soaks the sword,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.57,0:40:54.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,its draw speed increases. {hax! 飛天御剣流!}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.70,0:41:02.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The friction between the blade and sheath disappears, and Zerosen reaches the speed of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.52,0:41:07.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Zantou Namakura's limited hidden art, Zantou Gari!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.85,0:41:11.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The more it cuts, the faster it becomes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.29,0:41:13.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.81,0:41:16.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichika, let's make a tactical retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.91,0:41:19.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If we just leave him alone he'll bleed to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.75,0:41:20.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.50,0:41:21.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a chance to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.62,0:41:23.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That wouldn't be winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.71,0:41:25.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I won't win by chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.05,0:41:29.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty cool of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.03,0:41:36.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking at you, it makes me ashamed that I was hiding moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.08,0:41:37.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No more holding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.90,0:41:40.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you the full might of Kyotouryuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.28,0:41:41.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.84,0:41:48.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, actually there's one thing I want to ask you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.27,0:41:53.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Lil lady, you said that if I handed this Zantou over,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.78,0:41:56.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,you'd grant any wish of mine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.97,0:41:58.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.04,0:42:06.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, in exchange for this Zantou, can you restore Inaba to how it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.79,0:42:08.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.48,0:42:13.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The Shogunate has already decided the Tottori domain no longer exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.27,0:42:18.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And even if they hadn't, there's no way to reverse the desertification.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.96,0:42:20.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.34,0:42:27.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess that means I wasn't wrong in attacking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.31,0:42:28.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.08,0:42:31.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.59,0:42:33.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.22,0:42:36.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it for that "pride" stuff you were talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.84,0:42:39.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder at that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.19,0:42:42.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just said that on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.79,0:42:43.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take it seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.60,0:42:49.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to protect something.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.69,0:42:58.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But even though I wanted to protect something, this was the only thing left to me to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.84,0:43:00.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.72,0:43:04.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go then.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.33,0:43:05.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.61,0:43:08.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,my Zerosen's ready to go anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.47,0:43:12.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Observe Zerosen surpassing the speed of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.12,0:43:20.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you really have a hidden trick up your sleeve, show me that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.58,0:43:22.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I'll show you it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.08,0:43:28.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,However, by that point you'll have been torn into pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.39,0:43:30.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,On your marks...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.85,0:43:31.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Get set...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.88,0:43:32.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.21,0:43:34.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Zerosen formation: Ten lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.10,0:43:39.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Gyafun!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.99,0:43:43.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Everything is within Zerosen's range"?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.56,0:43:45.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.03,0:43:47.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't draw straight above your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.60,0:43:50.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kyotouryuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.48,0:43:55.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyotouryuu seventh hidden art: Rakka Rouzeki!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.48,0:43:55.87,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Scattered Blossoms
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.99,0:44:13.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So where are we going next?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.72,0:44:16.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.93,0:44:20.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Togame!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.47,0:44:22.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ignore me!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.10,0:44:24.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been like that since yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.45,0:44:27.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you injured somewhere when I kicked you?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.76,0:44:29.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so noisy!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.20,0:44:32.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop trying to speak so normally to someone when they're mad at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.70,0:44:37.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, I'd never have thought you'd use me as a wall to kick off of!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.23,0:44:40.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you're angry at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.30,0:44:41.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.84,0:44:47.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping the initial Iris chaining into Rose would do the job...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.92,0:44:51.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I really did just mean to use you as insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.27,0:44:53.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why couldn't you have told me that from the start,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.99,0:44:58.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,instead of saying grandiose things like "people with something to protect are strong" or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.11,0:45:01.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, that was just random babbling.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.59,0:45:02.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't babble!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.26,0:45:06.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,People who have something to protect are strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.21,0:45:09.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that that is not a means of becoming strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.31,0:45:14.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and that there are people who need something to protect in order to keep living...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.32,0:45:19.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichika learned that from this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.23,0:45:26.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The story of Katanagatari on this month and this evening ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.13,0:45:31.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me, you haven't actually seen Zantou's blade yet have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.44,0:45:33.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.53,0:45:34.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.81,0:45:40.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I couldn't follow Ginkaku's Zerosen with my eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.43,0:45:44.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,so I don't have the right to.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.33,0:45:47.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.60,0:45:51.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what'll happen to Inaba after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.10,0:45:51.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And Gekoku Castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.60,0:45:54.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.81,0:45:58.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,At this point it's already outside the Shogunate's jurisdiction,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.79,0:46:01.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,so it'll just rot away and perish.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.18,0:46:05.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, it'll last for ages to come, far longer than ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.57,0:46:12.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It might even continue on for a thousand more years, just not as a castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.64,0:46:14.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.86,0:46:19.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither swordsmen or their swords can win against nature, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.61,0:46:22.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it is, in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.04,0:46:23.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.72,0:46:27.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, Togame...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.60,0:46:29.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uneri's final line...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.43,0:46:30.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,it was really cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.96,0:46:36.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't only cool, it brought out his character.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.18,0:46:39.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you'd call a catchphrase?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.78,0:46:41.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a little off.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.24,0:46:44.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a line to fall by.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.73,0:46:46.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A final message,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.57,0:46:48.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,his last words before death.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.49,0:46:51.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You could call it his will.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.11,0:46:54.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's different from a catchphrase in that you only say it once in your whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.26,0:46:59.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not allowed to say it until you're ready to walk to the path to Hades.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.97,0:47:03.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.29,0:47:04.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.91,0:47:10.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly, one's final words are even more powerful than a catchphrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.60,0:47:13.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You only say it once in your lifetime, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.25,0:47:20.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,However understand that you, Shichika, are not allowed this one chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.05,0:47:24.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You needn't give any thought to your last words.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.90,0:47:38.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,At last, deep sleep is allowed me. {if this line is long and has to be split, use "At last, I can sleep soundly."}{Norg: maybe use that anyway, what kind of engrish is this line? lol} {that is not engrish you philistine!}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.55,0:49:15.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"However, by that point you'll have been torn into pieces" huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.55,0:49:17.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Although it wasn't high on my list of suggestions,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.67,0:49:20.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,if Shichika says he likes it, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.50,0:49:24.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, that plain Shichika will stand out a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.14,0:49:27.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, I'll try out this backwards talking thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.69,0:49:29.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Strategian the Togame,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.95,0:49:34.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shogunate Owari the of Shogun Yana... critical... the...
